  "text": "Successful plant growth, development, and response to environmental cues require precise control of gene expression. A key control stage of differential gene expression is transcriptional regulation mediated by transcriptional factors. Studies of plant transcription factors have focused mainly on activators [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , whereas repressors have just begun to receive attention.",
